    <h1>Referring Domain</h1>
    <p class="description">A unique external website that contains at least one backlink pointing to yours — counted once regardless of how many individual links that site sends. <strong>Diversity of referring domains outweighs raw backlink volume</strong> in Google's link evaluation.</p>
